ism</p><p class="sc-c-metadata__synopsis gs-u-hidden gel-brevier gs-u-mt- gs-u-mb">Melvyn Bragg and guests discuss relativism; a philosophy with no absolute truths.</p><ul class="gs-o-list-inline gs-o-list-inline--divided"><li class="sc-c-metadata__duration gs-u-mt- gel-brevier" aria-label="duration: 45 mins">45 mins</li></ul></div></div></a></div></li><li class="gs-u-align-top sc-c-carousel-item gel-9/24 gel-1/4@s gel-1/5@m gel-2/12@l gs-u-ml gs-u-ml+@s" data-id="p003hyck"><div class="sc-c-basic gel-1/1 gs-u-display-flex gs-u-align-left sc-u-flex-column sc-c-basic--hover-enabled"><a class="sc-c-basic__link gs-u-display-block sc-u-flex-grow sc-o-link play-c-exit-modal-bypass" href="/sounds/play/p003hycj" data-bbc-container="play_queue" data-bbc-content-label="content" data-bbc-event-type="select" data-bbc-metadata="{&quot;APP&quot;:&quot;responsive::sounds&quot;,&quot;BID&quot;:&quot;b006qykl&quot;,&quot;POS&quot;:&quot;3::92&quot;,&quot;PLQ&quot;:1}" data-bbc-result="p003hycj" data-bbc-source="bbc_radio_four" data-bbc-client-routed="true"><div class="sc-o-island"><div class="sc-c-rsimage sc-o-responsive-image sc-o-responsive-image--1by1 "><picture><source type="image/webp" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/160x160/p01gmzc9.jpg.webp 160w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/192x192/p01gmzc9.jpg.webp 192w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/224x224/p01gmzc9.jpg.webp 224w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/288x288/p01gmzc9.jpg.webp 288w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/576x576/p01gmzc9.jpg.webp 576w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 34vw,(max-width: 600px) 25vw,17vw"/><source type="image/jpg" srcSet="https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/160x160/p01gmzc9.jpg 160w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/192x192/p01gmzc9.jpg 192w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/224x224/p01gmzc9.jpg 224w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/288x288/p01gmzc9.jpg 288w,https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/576x576/p01gmzc9.jpg 576w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 34vw,(max-width: 600px) 25vw,17vw"/><img 